Q.4 Critique on a chart

https://www.vox.com/covid-19-coronavirus-us-response-trump/2020/5/18/21262265/georgia-covid-19-cases-declining-reopening

The x-axis of the bar chart does not present the date in chronological order, this gives a misleading message to the reader that the number of cases decreases over time.
